ackground: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">     设计风格</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">：扁平风</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; color: inherit; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">     特点</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">：简洁，清新，便于操作，用户体验好；</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; color: inherit; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">     弱点</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">页面布局有所欠缺</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">产品较少</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">；</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; color: inherit; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; color: inherit; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px;\">     首页见解</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px;\">：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; color: inherit; outline: 0px; text-align: center; background: transparent;\"><img alt=\"/templetes/meetiao/img/te1.jpg\" class=\"img-respon