: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">了Table</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; color: inherit; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; color: inherit; outline: 0px; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">     首页上能看到的栏目页有：“</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">宫廷共谱</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">巴马生铁锅</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">新疆馆</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">台湾馆</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">在导航</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">列表</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">上，其HTML中采用ul+li</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">方式</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">排列，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">也</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">非常合理，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font